{"tid":2242531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"正視聽，唔係鄭紀航想判針對政治人物行兇既藍絲坐監，而係感化報告反對，所以鄭才無奈判坐監","createTime":"2020-10-14T05:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T11:33:44.000Z","uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0797b4371370bf4cfe7af81f32051c9de2b685d3","tid":2242531,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"八旬老翁今年4月在中聯辦外以金屬尖鑿刺向「長毛」梁國雄腰窩，聲稱要替天行道，他早前在臨開審前認罪，惟強調是為「香港出頭」，並揚言「一個許智峯，一個黃之鋒，兩個遲早都要死」。而裁判官鄭紀航聞言仍指老翁熱愛社會，只因政見不同而犯案，先為老翁索取社會服務令報告，押至今早判刑，並讓老翁保釋。惟由於報告顯示老翁不適合擔任社會服務，鄭官今終判他入獄三個月六日。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/4MZ4VNLQMJAZ3PRXZGJ2LU32BI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2F4MZ4VNLQMJAZ3PRXZGJ2LU32BI%2F&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2rXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=4984694d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2F4MZ4VNLQMJAZ3PRXZGJ2LU32BI%2F&h=08fca2c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/4MZ4VNLQMJAZ3PRXZGJ2LU32BI/</a>"},{"pid":"7ae2f2cb1e0cea55b2bd618c5ed124a426947e41","tid":2242531,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae6bb783725e16e390c0df9754f34bd285b82c27","tid":2242531,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:29:18.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679bdeda2d5d9a56ddc151ecfc884275b122183e","tid":2242531,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"死紅官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46121d03556c7c48d98877325b6142c3c1ccf87f","tid":2242531,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime